= FixCacheBlockHtml

This extension extends Mage_CatalogRule_Model_Rule to automatic block html cache refresh and was created by the guys from Inchoo.net
http://inchoo.net/ecommerce/magento/magento-debugging/magento-how-to-fix-one-or-more-of-the-cache-types-are-invalidated-blocks-html-output-click-here-to-go-to-cache-management-and-refresh-cache-types/

== Compatibility
Successfully tested on Community Edition 1.6.x
Not tested on previous versions. But feel free to do so and inform me so this readme can be updated.

== Installation
* Download the source code and copy the files in the corresponding Magento folders; 
* mind that you merge the directoriesâ€¦ Do not replace the existing directories. :-)
* no Magento existing file is modified. 

